            <title>[CASSANDRA-10203] UnbufferedDataOutputstreamPlus.writeUTF fails for 0 length and &gt; 8190 length strings</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10203</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;No length is written for 0 length strings. Strings &amp;gt;8190 fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;EDIT: 2.0 and 2.1 are not affected.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12859444">CASSANDRA-10203</key>
